name: Flikken Maastricht
overview: Former Amsterdam police detective Floris Wolfs has been transferred to the police department of the south-Dutch country town Maastricht. His metropolitan experience nicely complements the local expertise of his new country colleagues, who know the folks. Slowly he fits in, while solving countless crimes together with his female partner Eva van Dongen.

production_companies.name: Warner Bros. International Television Production Netherlands

episodes.name: Resurrection
episodes.overview: Eva and Wolfs have a new team manager: Donna Martina. Their past gets in the way of proper functioning. Especially if Donna refuses to listen when Wolfs and Eva notice that they are not the only ones having trouble with Donna.

episodes.name: Murder at the gates of heaven
episodes.overview: Against her will Eva starts working as a team leader, leaving Wolfs to solve a murder case alone. The victim is a mysterious man with a fake personality. To find out why he was murdered, Wolfs must discover who he is.
